---

<section
    class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 sm:py-20 border-t border-gray-100 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Unmatched Performance</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-12">
        We benchmarked our API against traditional local generation. The results
        are scientifically indisputable.
    </p>

    <div
        class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex gap-2 sm:gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-medium" style="writing-mode: vertical-lr; transform: rotate(180deg);">Latency (ms)</span>
            </div>
        <div class="flex flex-1 items-end gap-2 sm:gap-4 h-48 sm:h-64">
            <div
                class="flex-1 h-full flex flex-col justify-end items-center min-w-0">
                <div
                    class="w-full max-w-[80px] bg-gray-200 rounded-t-lg transition-all hover:bg-gray-300"
                    style="height: 10%;">
                </div>
                <span
                    class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-2 font-medium text-center truncate w-full"
                    >Local (Slow)</span
                >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex-1 h-full flex flex-col justify-end items-center min-w-0">
                <div
                    class="w-full max-w-[80px] bg-gray-200 rounded-t-lg transition-all hover:bg-gray-300"
                    style="height: 15%;">
                </div>
                <span
                    class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-2 font-medium text-center truncate w-full"
                    >crypto.randomUUID()</span
                >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex-1 h-full flex flex-col justify-end items-center min-w-0">
                <div
                    class="w-full max-w-[80px] bg-blue-600 rounded-t-lg animate-pulse"
                    style="height: 100%;">
                </div>
                <span
                    class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-2 font-bold text-blue-600 text-center truncate w-full"
                    >UaaS (WEB SCALE)</span
                >
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[min(2.1vw,0.75rem)] text-gray-400">
            * Benchmarks performed while Barnaby was eating a very spicy
            burrito.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
